name: Total Potential Value - Faster Invoicing grouped by Inv. Company Code Text
query:
SELECT SUM ("Inv. Converted USD Amount") FILTER (WHERE ((SELECT LAST (END_TIME) FILTER (WHERE EVENT_NAME IN ('Create Billing Document'))) - (SELECT FIRST (END_TIME) FILTER (WHERE EVENT_NAME IN ('Record Goods Issue')))) > DURATION '1days') * 6 * 0.05 / 365 * 0.3 * 0.7 * 2, "Inv. Company Code Text"
FROM "defaultview-529"
